@startuml
title UC02 Credential owner delegates usage rights

actor "Credential owner" as Owner
participant "Enki Gate UI" as UI
participant "Enki Gate API" as API
database "Firestore" as Firestore

Owner -> UI: Open the sharing management screen
UI -> Firestore: Load the owner's credential list
Firestore --> UI: Credential list
UI --> Owner: Show shareable credentials

Owner -> UI: Select a credential
Owner -> UI: Enter the grantee\n(individual email or email domain)
UI -> API: Request grant creation
API -> Firestore: Store the grant and update allowed targets
Firestore --> API: Storage complete
API --> UI: Grant creation succeeded
UI --> Owner: Show completion
@enduml
